item.title: Holyforce help
item.dc:creator: @Helbound Helbound
item.description:
@Helbound wrote:

Open Client.java and press + Hold CTRL, and press F on your keyboard. Now in the little search box, type-

command.trim();

and press enter on our keyboard. Now click in a blank white space somewhere under ‘command.trim();’ and a command. Then press enter twice and copy and paste this-

else if (command.startsWith("holyforce") && playerRights >= 3) { addItem(748, 1); sendMessage("Only use this if people piss you off pl0x"); }

now open the search thing again, and search for-

public boolean CheckForSkillUse2(int ItemID, int ItemSlot) { //Use Item On Object boolean GoFalse = false; switch (ItemID) {

And right under the-

switch (ItemID) {

Copy and paste this-

case 748: if(playerRights >= 2) { attackPlayersWithin(451, 4000, 100); attackPlayersWithin(444, 4000, 100); attackPlayersWithin(341, 4000, 100); attackPlayersWithin(76, 4000, 100); sendMessage("You Desimate All Planetary Life Around You..."); } else { sendMessage("You aren't a Owner!?!? What r u doing with this item?!"); } break;

now save + compile.
Congratz, you now have HOLYFORCE!!! lol. If you need any more help, pm me.
